sequenceDiagram
accTitle: Mermaid advanced arrows
accDescr {
Demonstrates Mermaid bidirectional arrows and half-arrow variants mapped onto sequencer endpoint arrows.
From the project root, regenerate this Mermaid transform and SVG with:
node sequencer.js --mermaid -i test/mermaid-features/09-advanced-arrows/input.mmd -o -f -t test/mermaid-features/09-advanced-arrows
}
participant Caller
participant Service
Caller<<->>Service: Bidirectional filled [Mermaid: Caller<<->>Service]
Service<<-->>Caller: Bidirectional dotted filled [Mermaid: Service<<-->>Caller]
Caller-|\Service: Top half end [Mermaid: Caller-|\Service]
Service--|/Caller: Dotted bottom half end [Mermaid: Service--|/Caller]
Caller/|-Service: Reverse top half [Mermaid: Caller/|-Service]
Service\|--Caller: Dotted reverse bottom half [Mermaid: Service\|--Caller]
Caller-\Service: Top stick end [Mermaid: Caller-\Service]
Service--//Caller: Dotted bottom stick end [Mermaid: Service--//Caller]
Caller//-Service: Reverse top stick [Mermaid: Caller//-Service]
Service\\--Caller: Dotted reverse bottom stick [Mermaid: Service\\--Caller]
